     1 IDENTIFICATION    DIVISION.
     2 PROGRAM-ID.    EXERC4.
     3 AUTHOR.        YHAGO.
     4 INSTALLATION.    FATEC-SP.
     5 DATE-WRITTEN.    24/05/2025.
     6 DATE-COMPILED. 26-May-25 20:17.
     7 SECURITY.    APENAS O AUTOR PODE MODIFICAR.
     8
     9 ENVIRONMENT    DIVISION.
    10 CONFIGURATION    SECTION.
    11 SOURCE-COMPUTER.    IBM-PC.
    12 OBJECT-COMPUTER.    IBM-PC.
    13 SPECIAL-NAMES.    DECIMAL-POINT IS COMMA.
    14
    15 INPUT-OUTPUT     SECTION.
    16 FILE-CONTROL.
    17     SELECT CAD-CLIENTE ASSIGN TO DISK
    18     ORGANIZATION IS LINE SEQUENTIAL.
    19     SELECT ARQ-SORT ASSIGN TO DISK.
    20     SELECT REL-GERAL ASSIGN TO DISK
    21     ORGANIZATION IS LINE SEQUENTIAL.
    22
    23 DATA    DIVISION.
    24 FILE    SECTION.
    25 FD CAD-CLIENTE
    26     LABEL RECORD STANDARD
    27     VALUE OF FILE-ID IS "CADENT.DAT".
    28 01 REG-CLIENTE.
    29     02 CODIGO-ENT    PIC 9(03).
    30     02 CPF-ENT       PIC 9(11).
    31     02 NOME-ENT      PIC X(30).
    32     02 ESTADO-ENT    PIC X(02).
    33     02 CIDADE-ENT    PIC X(30).
    34     02 EMAIL-ENT    PIC X(30).
    35 SD ARQ-SORT.
    36 01 REG-SORT.
    37     02 CODIGO-SORT    PIC 9(03).
    38     02 CPF-SORT       PIC 9(11).
    39     02 NOME-SORT      PIC X(30).
    40     02 ESTADO-SORT    PIC X(02).
    41     02 CIDADE-SORT    PIC X(30).
    42     02 EMAIL-SORT    PIC X(30).
    43 FD REL-GERAL
    44     LABEL RECORD  OMITTED.
    45 01 REG-ATR      PIC X(80).
    46 WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
    47     77 FIM-ARQ-ENTRADA    PIC X(03) VALUE "NAO".
    48     77 FIM-ARQ-SAIDA    PIC X(03) VALUE "NAO".
    49     77 CT-LIN       PIC 9(02) VALUE 20.
    50     77 CT-PAG       PIC 9(02) VALUE ZEROS.
    51     77 CPF-STR    PIC X(11) VALUE ZEROS.
    52     77 DIG01      PIC X(1) VALUE ZEROS.
    53     77 DIG02      PIC X(1) VALUE ZEROS.
    54     77 ESTADO     PIC X(02) VALUE ZEROS.
    55     77 CIDADE     PIC X(30) VALUE ZEROS.
    56 01 CAB.
    57     02 FILLER     PIC X(80) VALUE SPACES.
* Microsoft COBOL Version 4.5        L2.4 revision 002 26-May-25 20:17 Page   2
*                                      EXERC4.CBL
    58 01 CAB-01.
    59     02 FILLER     PIC X(20) VALUE SPACES.
    60     02 FILLER     PIC X(37)
    61         VALUE "RELAÇĂO DE CLIENTES POR ESTADO/CIDADE".
    62     02 FILLER     PIC X(5) VALUE SPACES.
    63     02 FILLER     PIC X(05) VALUE "PAG. ".
    64     02 VAR-PAG    PIC ZZ9.
    65 01 CAB-ESTADO.
    66     02 FILLER     PIC X(08) VALUE "ESTADO: ".
    67     02 VAR-ESTADO PIC X(02).
    68 01 CAB-CIDADE.
    69     02 FILLER     PIC X(08) VALUE "CIDADE: ".
    70     02 VAR-CIDADE PIC X(30).
    71 01 CAB-02.
    72     02 FILLER     PIC X(04) VALUE "CPF".
    73     02 FILLER     PIC X(20) VALUE SPACES.
    74     02 FILLER     PIC X(04) VALUE "NOME".
    75     02 FILLER     PIC X(27) VALUE SPACES.
    76     02 FILLER     PIC X(05) VALUE "EMAIL".
    77 01 DETALHE.
    78     02 VAR-CPF    PIC 999.999.999.
    79     02 FILLER     PIC X(01) VALUE "-".
    80     02 VAR-DIG01  PIC 9.
    81     02 VAR-DIG02  PIC 9.
    82     02 FILLER     PIC X(10) VALUE SPACES.
    83     02 VAR-NOME   PIC X(30).
    84     02 FILLER     PIC X(1) VALUE SPACES.
    85     02 VAR-EMAIL  PIC X(30).
    86 PROCEDURE    DIVISION.
    87 PGM-EX05.
    88 SORT    ARQ-SORT
    89         ON ASCENDING KEY ESTADO-SORT
    90         ON ASCENDING KEY CIDADE-SORT
    91         ON ASCENDING KEY CPF-SORT
    92         USING CAD-CLIENTE
    93         OUTPUT PROCEDURE ROT-RELATORIO.
    94 STOP    RUN.
    95
    96 ROT-RELATORIO SECTION.
    97     PERFORM INICIO-SAIDA.
    98     PERFORM PRINCIPAL-SAIDA
    99             UNTIL FIM-ARQ-SAIDA EQUAL "SIM".
   100     PERFORM FIM-SAIDA.
   101
   102 INICIO-SAIDA SECTION.
   103     OPEN OUTPUT REL-GERAL.
   104     PERFORM LEITURA-SAIDA.
   105
   106 LEITURA-SAIDA SECTION.
   107     RETURN ARQ-SORT INTO REG-SORT
   108      AT END MOVE 'SIM' TO FIM-ARQ-SAIDA.
   109
   110 PRINCIPAL-SAIDA SECTION.
   111     PERFORM GRAVACAO-SAIDA.
   112     PERFORM LEITURA-SAIDA.
   113
   114 GRAVACAO-SAIDA SECTION.
   115     IF CT-LIN GREATER THAN 19
* Microsoft COBOL Version 4.5        L2.4 revision 002 26-May-25 20:17 Page   3
*                                      EXERC4.CBL
   116         PERFORM CABECALHO-01
   117     END-IF.
   118     IF NOT(ESTADO-SORT = ESTADO) OR NOT(CIDADE-SORT = CIDADE)
   119          PERFORM CABECALHO-02
   120     END-IF.
   121     MOVE ESTADO-SORT TO ESTADO.
   122     MOVE CIDADE-SORT TO CIDADE.
   123     PERFORM DETALHES.
   124 CABECALHO-01   SECTION.
   125     ADD 1         TO CT-PAG.
   126     MOVE CT-PAG   TO VAR-PAG.
   127     MOVE SPACES   TO REG-ATR.
   128     WRITE REG-ATR AFTER ADVANCING PAGE.
   129     WRITE REG-ATR FROM CAB-01 AFTER ADVANCING 1 LINE.
   130     WRITE REG-ATR FROM CAB AFTER ADVANCING 1 LINE.
   131     MOVE 1  TO CT-LIN.
   132 CABECALHO-02 SECTION.
   133     MOVE ESTADO-SORT TO VAR-ESTADO.
   134     MOVE CIDADE-SORT TO VAR-CIDADE.
   135     IF CT-LIN = 1
   136         WRITE REG-ATR FROM CAB-ESTADO AFTER ADVANCING 1 LINE
   137         ADD 4         TO CT-LIN
   138     ELSE
   139         WRITE REG-ATR FROM CAB-ESTADO AFTER ADVANCING 2 LINE
   140         ADD 5         TO CT-LIN
   141     END-IF.
   142     WRITE REG-ATR FROM CAB-CIDADE AFTER ADVANCING 1 LINE.
   143     WRITE REG-ATR FROM CAB-02 AFTER ADVANCING 2 LINE.
   144
   145 DETALHES SECTION.
   146     MOVE CPF-SORT TO CPF-STR.
   147     MOVE CPF-STR(10:1) TO DIG01.
   148     MOVE CPF-STR(11:1) TO DIG02.
   149     MOVE CPF-SORT(1:9)    TO VAR-CPF.
   150     MOVE DIG01 TO VAR-DIG01.
   151     MOVE DIG02 TO VAR-DIG02.
   152     MOVE NOME-SORT TO VAR-NOME
   153     MOVE EMAIL-SORT      TO VAR-EMAIL.
   154     WRITE REG-ATR FROM DETALHE AFTER ADVANCING 1 LINE.
   155     ADD 1         TO CT-LIN.
   156
   157 FIM-SAIDA SECTION.
   158     CLOSE REL-GERAL.
